The Kukui Cup is a competition between various residence halls with three major goals:
<ol>
<li> Help residents to learn more about energy and ways that they can use it more efficiently and effectively;
<li> Provide a fun and interesting competition where residents can win prizes by saving energy and performing energy-related activities;
<li> Understand more about the ways in which people are motivated (or not) to conserve energy.
</ol>
